OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with patchy cloud and largely
OL,7,Fclear skies. Remaining dry with clear
OL,8,Fspells overnight, leading to a touch
OL,9,Fof frost in rural spots in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FMuch of the region will be dry
OL,12,Fand bright with the best of the
OL,13,Fsunshine to the south and east of
OL,14,FGlasgow. Argyll cloudier, with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
